### Login as admin
POST http://jwt.battistas.org/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "admin",
    "password": "admin"
}

### Login as user1
POST http://jwt.battistas.org/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "user1",
    "password": "password1"
}

### Test user endpoint (requires any valid JWT)
GET http://jwt.battistas.org/user
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Test protected endpoint (requires admin JWT)
GET http://jwt.battistas.org/protected
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Get JWT token information and details
GET http://jwt.battistas.org/token-info
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Validate JWT token via POST request
POST http://jwt.battistas.org/validate-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "token": "<token>"
}

### Test with invalid token
POST http://jwt.battistas.org/validate-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "token": "invalid.jwt.token"
}

### Test without token field
POST http://jwt.battistas.org/validate-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nottoken": "missing field test"
}

